\v 2 \x + \xo 1:2: \xt Acts 18:1.\x*\add It's written\add* to God's assemblyВҰ113016 there in CorinthВҰ113030вҖ”to those believers in Messiah Yeshua who've been declared guiltless \add and\add* who've been calledВҰ113031 to live holy lives, along with all those who appeal to the power of ourВҰ113041 and theirВҰ113047 \nd masterВҰ113040 Yeshua Messiah\nd*, everywhereВҰ113045.
