\v 13 We don'tВҰ113808 speakВҰ113807 about these things from our humanВҰ113811 wisdomВҰ113812, but rather, saying what \add God's\add* \nd spiritВҰ113817\nd* teachesвҖ”teaching spiritual things from spiritual \add sources\add*.
