\v 16 Don't you realise that you \add yourselves\add* are God's templeВҰ114128, and that God's \nd spiritВҰ114133\nd* lives \add inside\add* you all?\x + \xo 3:16: \xt 1Cor 6:19; 2Cor 6:16.\x*
