\p
\v 1 Now brothersВҰ116769 and sistersВҰ116769, I don'tВҰ116768 want youВҰ116767 all to be ignorant about how ourВҰ116773 Jewish ancestorsВҰ116772 sheltered underВҰ116775 the cloudВҰ116777 and then they all passedВҰ116784 through the seaВҰ116783,\x + \xo 10:1: a \xt Exo 13:21-22; \xo b \xt Exo 14:22-29.\x*
