\v 3 ThenВҰ120302, when I arriveВҰ120303, I'llВҰ120312 \add write\add* lettersВҰ120310 to send with those you recommend to take to Jerusalem with yourВҰ120316 gift,
\v 4 butВҰ120321 if it's appropriate for me to go as well, thenВҰ120321 theyВҰ120330 can travel with me.
