\p
\v 5 After I've been to Macedonia I'llВҰ120332 come there. \add Yes,\add* I'm going through Macedonia,\x + \xo 16:5: \xt Acts 19:21.\x*
\v 6 butВҰ120345 perhaps I'llВҰ120348 spend some time with youвҖ”maybe even the whole winterВҰ120351. That way, you all could help me on my way whereverВҰ120356 I decide to go next,
\v 7 because I don't want to seeВҰ120367 you all now \add just\add* in passing, but I'd like to stay with you all for a some timeВҰ120371 if the \nd masterВҰ120378\nd* permitsВҰ120380.
\p
\v 8 But I'llВҰ120381 stay \add here\add* at EphesusВҰ120384 untilВҰ120385 the Pentecost celebrations\x + \xo 16:8: \xt Lev 23:15-21; Deu 16:9-11.\x*
\v 9 becauseВҰ120389 a wide doorВҰ120388 has openedВҰ120391 for me to be effective \add here\add*, even though many are opposingВҰ120396 \add me\add*.
\p
\v 10 Now if TimothyВҰ120401 arrives, make sure that he has nothing for him to be afraid of there, becauseВҰ120409 he's doingВҰ120412 \nd Yahweh's\nd* workВҰ120410 just like me.\x + \xo 16:10: \xt 1Cor 4:17.\x*
\v 11 So don't let anyoneВҰ120418 despise him, butВҰ120423 help him on his way in peaceВҰ120426, so that he can comeВҰ120428 to me becauseВҰ120432 I'm expecting him along with the brothersВҰ120436.
\p
\v 12 And then concerning the brotherВҰ120441 ApollosВҰ120439, I strongly urged him to go to you with the brothersВҰ120454. He didn'tВҰ120457 want to go at the present time, butВҰ120438 he'll go when he has \add another\add* opportunityВҰ120467.
\s1 Final messages and greetings
